high_descs: Turn right then head towards the table.
Pick up the silver knife from the table.
Turn right then head towards the door, turn left then head towards the sink.
Place the knife into the right side of the sink.
Turn all the way around then head towards the door, turn right then head towards the wall, then right towards the table.
Pick up the knife next to the tea kettle.
Turn around then turn left then head towards the door. Turn left then head towards the sink.
Place the knife into the sink on top of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two knives into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go to counter.
Pick up knife in front of the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn right then left, proceed to sink across room.
Place knife in lower right hand corner of sink.
Turn around, proceed to door.  Turn right and proceed to wall.  Turn right to face counter with kettle and knife on it.
Pick up knife from counter, to the right of the kettle.
Turn around, proceed to wall.  Turn left, proceed to door on your right.  Turn left, go to sink.
Put knife in sink directly criss cross over the first knife.
anns.task_desc: Move two knives to a sink.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, turn right at the door and face the white counter with the two knives.
Pick up the butter knife to the left of the sharp knife.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the knife down in the sink in front of the tomato.
Turn around and walk back over to the white counter and face the counter that's behind the two stools.
Pick up the butter knife to the right of the kettle.
Walk back over to the sink.
Place the butter knife in the sink behind the first knife.
anns.task_desc: Place two butter knives in the sink.
